Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別攻擊也太反常…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃國之防人
