Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一連串事件的幕後黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是風鳴機關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我也相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人那麼笨拙怎麼可能做出背叛這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒有懷疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐是我們重要的同伴Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是被那雙魔眼給…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}速至司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此乃與吾國相稱之神之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藉由直通回饋系統之腦控行將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(542.666,670.333)}Direct Feedback System
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屆時便是新時代之威懾力誕生之日
