Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是如何造出新Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此非Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃神獸鏡之Faust-Robe是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然鑄就此物者已不知葬身何處矣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中迴響著非如此不可的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時便毫不猶豫地行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉念想來　那真的是正確的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何故未將其斬盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷　但切莫迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那般弱小之內心終難擔大任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為守家護國化作惡鬼便是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲斷無從拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　突然叫你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間緊迫　有新的任務要交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經由多日的秘密調查以及政治手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對風鳴宗家強行搜查的準備完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風鳴宗家是你們和翼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　已經刻不容緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因違反風鳴訃堂親自推行的護國災害派遣法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受日本政府所託加以逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據情況　當場擊斃也已被批准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊斃　對翼也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故而做出了此事不能交給因違規正在禁閉的響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及其他未成年成員的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只叫了瑪利亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是任務　但恕我不能苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者就是將心置於刀刃之下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何　血親相殘都是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了將翼綁回來才和你們一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然中途就意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎麼想都是我根本幫不上忙的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你說要我說給你聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這麼說啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許是被詛咒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我權限內的安防措施都可以解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡速拘捕風鳴訃堂及相關人員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alca-NOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪利亞　Amalgam暫時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想吃禁閉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若再違反協定 S.O.N.G.今後或將無法在日本行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於預定時間開始交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但行動限制尚未完全解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊搜查　扣押相關證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請隨我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搖尾乞憐於聯合國之逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何事竟敢恬面至此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自是為勸阻您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　這才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有太多事等你解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對風鳴訃堂唯命是從就是你所謂的防人之道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(855,670.333)}守
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(895,670.333)}護
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(935,670.333)}眾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(975,670.333)}生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之力亦乃為此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等冷血的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此間安容爾多言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的親密戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你生而為你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼神之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以你一己之力守護眾生的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋需贅言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾生無力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此　更需絕世之力加以守護
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無力就需要守護　這是何等傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所言何意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話簡直像說不守護什麼人就無法自立一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候開始從守護他人變成獨善其身的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護庇羸弱不成其為理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我又是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天如癡如狂地防人防人不離口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白　我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爾若一心取吾性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無能若斯　枉為吾子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在外面打得正熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我們的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把神之力的管理權限改為我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風鳴訃堂如此輕易拋棄我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不報復我嚥不下這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　先將直通回饋系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(701.333,672.999)}Direct Feedback System
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎　米蕾婭克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到大家的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吾身邊　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若為防人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若仍流有風鳴之血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經連應倚仗什麼都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印　啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爾亦欲令風鳴蒙羞乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不肖逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟又有犬子現身乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親您為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓別的男人以你的父親自居啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並非因眾生無力而加以守護
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因為他們有值得守護的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要牢記於心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命已嗚呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忤逆犯上　業有應得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得守護的價值究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚不成熟的我暫且無從得知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請您傾聽我的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:17:00.69,IN_T_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Imyuteus amenohabakiri tron
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1262,21)}風輪火斬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,64)}卻有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以肉身凌駕於Gear之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲無從守護世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相通相解不過癡人說夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爾頌此等狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何顏以對拋顱灑血為國捐軀之先烈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻仍執迷不悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕　趕上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾生之刃群蜘蛛竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國之所需並非防人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是護國惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾捨命化護國惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爾亦終墮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護國惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你也墮為惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就無顏面對老哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震？這震動是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的禁閉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了　馬上趕回總部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事　小問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒法為你做什麼的廢材老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一能說給女兒聽的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣一句話對沒有骨氣的我不知何時變成了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把一件事當成詛咒或是祝福全在一念之間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詛咒…說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　你看　那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「咒」和「祝」的讀音其實很像的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以互為正反…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我說的話也不都是錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年的這時候肯定會變成名言的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確會變成名言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧　響
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦　爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉麵很好吃
